name: om admin look
author: Siddharth Singh

sections.description:
Add bootstrap to admin panel, useful if you need to use it in other admin files, with copyright message at footer for admin panel, good if you sharing something copyrighted with your users which have admin access.

Please provide me five star review.

*2:Now activate the plugin *Form wordpress admin panel view A
